description:
~ An enchanting, sparkling and interactive experience fit for Royalty ~
~~ 150+ beautiful princesses screens in 8 fun unique games ~~
~~~ No.1 Free Education App in the USA, UK and 45 Countries around the world ~~~
~~~~ Over 2,000,000 Downloads! Selected New & Noteworthy by Apple ~~~~

Come and enjoy a royal treat with Princess Coloring Book; The perfect app for your little princess. Here you will find a captivating and interactive experience with 8 unique and magical games games. Including 50+ colorful, lovable princesses and more than 150 screens for an enjoyable and enchanting painting experience.

-  -  - 8 Royal Games and Activities inside! -  -  -
+ Magic Draw - Slide your finger on the drawing area to magically color a princess and watch her come to life.
+Coloring Book - Handmade illustrated coloring pages of the most beloved princesses. Finger paint or fill area with color to complete lovely princess coloring pages.
+ Maze Challenge -  Help the princesses find their way across the maze and reach their castle. 
+ Sticker Book - Interact with the HD illustrated princesses on screen while you can finger paint with colors and fill area with paint buckets. 
+ Mix and Match  - The princesses got all mixed up, help match the parts and put the colorful princesses back together.
+ Princess Run - Join Princess Penny on her royal stroll through the palace forest. Help her collect all the boxes and find out which beautiful princess is hiding behind them. 
+ Puzzle Fun - Enjoy 50+ colorful, intuitive princess shaped puzzles. 
+ Memory Match - Can you find the princesses which are exactly the same? find all the princess pairs to win the game.
